dcs.climate.tip.checker: Can check the climate in the right-click position
dcs.tip.null_item1: Null items may be registered in the recipe.
dcs.tip.null_item2: Check out the settings for this recipe.
dcs.tip.container.ownable: The Owner can lock this tile and restrict its use to the Owner or ServerOP only, and stops unloading of the hopper.
dcs.tip.device.sorter.type.phrase: Phrase (filter items display name) is included as part of the item name or tag name

dcs.tip.fertile.fertile: You can fertilize this block to promoting crop growth.
dcs.tip.faucet.desc: It generates water and sends it to the liquid tank/pipe directly below.

dcs.tip.energy.rs_signal_machine: Activated by an RS signal or a right click.
dcs.tip.energy.item_aspirator.desc: Collects dropped items within a 9x9x9 area in front.

dcs.tip.process.error.no_0: Process Error: Cannot unload material container!

dcs.tip.memory_coord: Used for HaC machines with coordinate registration: Registers coordinates into the machine.
dcs.tip.empty_pack: Right-click: Can be filled with water or milk.

dcs.tip.sap: It can be collected using a Spile.
